newsletter.title: Habitat for Humanity Volunteering Event
newsletter.description: SHPE Austin partnered with Habitat For Humanity on June 11th to help local area families obtain affordable housing. Members participated in construction, landscaping, and painting activities. This was a fun and memorable experience!

newsletter.title: Elections Meeting
newsletter.description: Join SHPE Austin for 2016-17 elections meeting this Thursday at 7PM at the HEB Community Room (1801 E 51st St, Austin, TX 78723). We will be electing our new executive board, which includes the following positions: President, Vice-President, Treasurer, and Secretary. If you would like to nominate someone, including yourself, please email your nominations by Wed. June 29th by 11PM CST. Free food and drinks will be provided.

newsletter.title: SHPE Summer Event
newsletter.description: Every summer SHPE Austin gets together to host a cook-out. This event will be open to all existing and prospective members. Stay tuned for more details in the coming July newsletter.
